title: 685. Reaction to Julio Jones' Trade & Top Pass-catching Duos by Division
itunes:title: 685. Reaction to Julio Jones' Trade & Top Pass-catching Duos by Division
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the Tennessee Titans trading for wide receiver Julio Jones and look at his value (2:36). Then, the pair pick the top pass-catching duos by going through each division in the league (21:10). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
